Thanks for downloading migasfree server.

This process will create and install the packages:

    * django-ajax-select
    * migasfree-server


1.- Download create-migasfree-server-package file:

    # wget --no-check-certificate https://github.com/agacias/migasfree/raw/new_ui/bin/create-migasfree-server-package


2.- Choose code branch (master by default):

    # bash create-migasfree-server-package new_ui


3.- Check migasfree/settings.py (p.e. /usr/shared/pyshared/migasfree/settings.py):

    * Database parameters
    * Secret key
    * Organization name
    * Time zone
    * ...

4.- Execute this script to create initial data (default superuser is admin:admin):

    # migasfree-server-from-scratch


And enjoy migasfree experience!!!
